videos.headline: Harris bursts 66 yards for Miami TD
videos.description: Cam'Ron Harris slips through the UAB defense and jets down the field to easily score a 66-yard rushing touchdown for Miami.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harris bursts 66 yards for Miami TD) 2020/09/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: King scrambles for 12-yard Miami TD run
videos.description: D'Eriq King finds an opening and uses his speed to exploit the defense and score a 12-yard touchdown to give Miami a 14-7 lead over UAB.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (King scrambles for 12-yard Miami TD run) 2020/09/10 ESHEET
